dc_title_s: Jitchi sokuryō Owari no Kuni Mikawa no Kuni shichōson shinzu: zen; Odagiri Takeo.; Owari no Kuni Mikawa no Kuni shichōson shinzu;Title on map: Bi-San shichōson shinzu
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Copperplate print. Relief shown by hachures. 3 insets: 1) Nagoya 1:36,000 -- 2) Toyohashi 1:20,000 -- 3) Okazaki 1:20,000. Includes distance chart, list of town names and officials, etc. 1 map: col.; 76 x 102 cm., folded in covers 20 x 14 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
